ed="T" n="0785c18"/><anchor n="T.50.2061.0785c18"/><head><date from-iso="+0907-06-10" key="j20524952058534" to-iso="+0923-12-22">梁</date><placeName key="PL000000057277">福州玄沙院</placeName><persName key="A008370">師備</persName>傳</head><p><lb
ed="T" n="0785c19"/><persName key="A008370">釋師備</persName>，俗姓<name>謝</name>，<placeName key="PL000000017166">閩</placeName>人也。少而憨黠<ptr type="glossary" target="#g50"/>，酷好垂<lb
ed="T" n="0785c20"/>釣<ptr target="#n403"/>，往往泛小艇<placeName key="PL000000056760">南臺江</placeName>自娛。其舟若虛，同<lb
ed="T" n="0785c21"/>類不我測也。一日，忽發出塵意，投釣棄舟，<lb
ed="T" n="0785c22"/>上<placeName key="PL000000057110">芙蓉山</placeName>出家，<date from-iso="+0860-01-31" key="j20351992035582" to-iso="+0861-02-17"><name>咸通</name>初年</date>也。後於<placeName key="PL000000018582">豫章開<lb
ed="T" n="0785c23"/>元寺</placeName>具戒<ptr target="#n1706"/>。還歸故里，山門力役，無不率先。<lb
ed="T" n="0785c24"/>布<anchor xml:id="beg0785003"/><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>衲</sic><corr>納</corr></choice><anchor xml:id="end0785003"/>添麻，芒鞵續草，減食而食，語默有常，<lb
ed="T" n="0785c25"/>人咸畏之，汪汪大度，雖<persName key="A010365">研</persName>、<persName key="A023044">桑</persName>巧計不能量<lb
ed="T" n="0785c26"/>也<ptr type="glossary" target="#g51"/>。<persName key="A008370">備</persName>同學法兄，則<placeName key="PL000000017136">雪峯</placeName><persName key="A003677">存<roleName>師</roleName></persName>也，一再相逢，<persName key="A003677">存</persName><lb
ed="T" n="0785c27"/>多許與，故目之為<persName key="A008370">備</persName>頭陀焉。有日，謔之曰：<lb
ed="T" n="0785c28"/>「<ref type="person" target="#A008370">頭陀</ref>何不遍參去？」<persName key="A008370">備</persName>對曰：「<persName key="A001361">達磨</persName>不來<ref type="place" target="#PL000000000083">東土</ref>，<lb
ed="T" n="0785c29"/><ref type="person" target="#A003881">二祖</ref>不往<ref type="place" target="#PL000000048207">西天</ref>。」<persName key="A003677">存</persName>深器重<ref type="person" target="#A008370">之</ref>。<anchor xml:id="beg0785004"/>先<anchor xml:id="end0785004"/>開荒<placeName key="PL000000017136">雪峯</placeName>，<pb ed="T" n="0786a" xml:id="T50.2061.0786a"/><lb
ed="T" n="0786a01"/><persName key="A008370">備</persName>多率力<ptr target="#n1707"/>。<persName key="A003732">王<roleName>氏</roleName></persName>始有<placeName key="PL000000056178">閩</placeName>土，奏賜紫衣，號<persName key="A008370">宗<lb
ed="T" n="0786a02"/>一大師</persName>。以<date key="j20530622053062" when-iso="+0908-12-28"><name>開平</name>二年戊辰十一月二十七日</date><lb
ed="T" n="0786a03"/>示疾而終，春秋七十四，僧臘四十四<ptr target="#n1708"/>。<placeName key="PL000000056178">閩越</placeName><persName key="A003732"><roleName>忠<lb
ed="T" n="0786a04"/>懿王</roleName>王<roleName>氏</roleName></persName>樹塔<ptr target="#n1709"/>。<persName key="A008370">備</persName>三十年演化，禪侶七百許<lb
ed="T" n="0786a05"/>人，得其法者眾，推<persName key="A010683">桂琛</persName>為神足矣。至今<lb
ed="T" n="0786a06"/><ref type="place" target="#PL000000011455">浙之左右</ref>山門盛傳此宗，法嗣繁衍矣。其於<lb
ed="T" n="0786a07"/>建立透過大乘初門。<placeName key="PL000000000197">江表</placeName>學人無不乘風<lb
ed="T" n="0786a08"/>偃草歟。</p>
